task.summary: 2.2.1 : Exit on some actions in SysService
2.2.2 : Log path can be specified. Test classes added
2.2.7 : Added onSleep for background processes in SysSrv and Recoded part of JDBCConnector. Removed DBType.NONE
2.2.8 : Improved Command and removed Closure objects
2.2.9 : Added missing data types in DB
2.2.10 : Converted abstract Cache into Generic Class
2.2.10.5 : Added Cache expiration and Singleton CacheObj
2.2.11+ : Added compare script and fixed minor differences
2.2.13 : Added smtps, replyTo and fromName to SMTP
2.2.14: SysService now accepts custom arguments. getAction was removed. SMTP SSL related code is now automatic.
2.2.16: Replaced all ArrayLists for List and HashMap for Map
2.2.16.1 : Removed type enforcement in insert to allow use of groovy Maps

MESSAGE.value: 2.2.2 : Log path can be specified. Test classes added
2.2.7 : Added onSleep for background processes in SysSrv and Recoded part of JDBCConnector. Removed DBType.NONE
2.2.8 : Improved Command and removed Closure objects
2.2.9 : Added missing data types in DB
2.2.10 : Converted abstract Cache into Generic Class
2.2.10.5 : Added Cache expiration and Singleton CacheObj
2.2.10.6 : Added notFound interface in Cache to prevent executing that code everytime
2.2.11+ : Added compare script and fixed minor differences
2.2.13 : Added smtps, replyTo and fromName to SMTP
2.2.14: SysService now accepts custom arguments. getAction was removed. SMTP SSL related code is now automatic.
2.2.16: Replaced all ArrayLists for List and HashMap for Map
2.2.16.1 : Removed type enforcement in insert to allow use of groovy Maps
